text: A nice peaceful neighbourhood park for the nearby residents. A well-intended AED (Automated External Defibrillator) is afixed at the shelter.
A place to rest and shelter from rain.. Trees and plants around a very cooling place with shelter.
Cozy and mostly shaded. Family friendly with a kids play area and workout equipments. Many neighbours bring their kids and dogs here
Good neighborhood park, well maintained equipment for kids. Has swings, slide and decent area for kids to run about
Nice cozy park. Clean and quiet. Good for a quick getaway and exercise for kids
